-- ds.page: `get-current-tasks` API

This API fetch the information from GitHub project about current sprint. A
GitHub project can have multiple issues listed, in this API we fetch individual
issue statuses and their tracking from attached PR(s).

-- ds.h1: API Input

-- ds.h2: `token`

API security token, that only known people can call this API or to it prevent
from calling unauthorized people.


-- ds.h1: API Output


-- ds.code:
lang: ftd

